{"type":"message","id":"2abe507a","parentId":"316b04aa","timestamp":"2026-06-02T02:40:41.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to analyze a bug/error log they've shared. This is a red-colored error message that appears to be about a WeChat URL. Let me look at what we have:\n\nThe error is about a `WeChatUrl` - it's a `weixin://` deep link URL with encoded parameters. Let me decode the URL parameters to understand what this is about.\n\nThe URL: `weixin://dl/business/?appid=wx2af2be9a3b47ff43&path=pages/reward-center/index&env_version=release&query=activityKey%3DYYZY_CCG_JOIN_WECOM%26gameId%3D5199%26key%3d...`\n\nThis seems to be a WeChat Mini Program deep link. The error itself doesn't give much context - it just prints the URL. To analyze this properly, I need more context:\n\n1. Where is this error coming from? (which file in the project)\n2. What's the full error message?\n3. What's the context around this error?\n\nBut the user just shared this error line. Let me think about what I can do...\n\nActually, the user just pasted a single error line. Let me search the codebase for where this error is logged to understand the context better.\n\nLet me search the project for \"WeChatUrl\" to find where this error is coming from.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，这条错误信息只有输出没有上下文。我来搜一下项目里哪里打这个日志的，看看具体逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Nb00UC6Xxir1Mhq42p6G5118","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Select-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\**\\*.cs' -Pattern 'WeChatUrl' -CaseSensitive | Select-Object -First 30\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":997,"output":430,"cacheRead":19840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21267,"cost":{"input":0.00013958000000000002,"output":0.00012040000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00055552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008155}},"stopReason":"t