{"type":"message","id":"c0758c7f","parentId":"b3f2b2cc","timestamp":"2026-06-02T02:41:03.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems like this URL construction or logging is not in the codebase at all. It might be in:\n1. A third-party SDK\n2. The Lua script resource bundles (which are built)\n3. A different project\n\nLet me give a helpful analysis based on what I can see from the error message itself.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，这个错误在项目代码里搜不到——说明不是我们直接写的代码，可能是第三方 SDK 或游戏运行时环境层的。\n\n不过从这条日志本身可以分析出一些东西：\n\n---\n\n**这条 URL 是什么：**\n- 一个**微信小程序跳转链接**（`weixin://dl/business/`）\n- 跳转到 `pages/reward-center/index`\n- AppID: `wx2af2be9a3b47ff43`\n- 参数里带了个 `activityKey=YYZY_CCG_JOIN_WECOM`（加入企微的奖励活动）\n\n**URL 解码后关键参数：**\n```\nappid=wx2af2be9a3b47ff43\npath=pages/reward-center/index\nenv_version=release\nquery=\n  activityKey=YYZY_CCG_JOIN_WECOM\n  gameId=5199\n  key=Q2qUBzXtjvqVncLxz4V35b4zGtFneYTQAoAOasEm7zS... （很长一串加密串）\n```\n\n**可能的问题点：**\n\n1. **URL 太长** — `key` 参数加密后的字符串很长，总 URL 超出了微信跳转链接的长度限制\n2. **编码问题** — URL 里混用了 `%2f`(标准) 和 `%2F`，有的微信 SDK 版本对大小写敏感\n3. **`env_version=release`** — 链接指定了正式环境，但你可能是在调试环境跑的，微信会拒绝\n4. **加密 key 过期/无效** — `key` 是加密的签名参数，如果生成方和校验方算法不一致就会报错\n\n**建议排查方向：**\n- 这个 URL 是**哪里拼接的**？是 C# 端还是 Lua 端？还是服务端返回的？\n- 日志是在什么时机打出来的？（打开某个页面/点击某个按钮后？）\n- 完整的堆栈/上下文日志还有吗？光这一行信息量不够\n\n能把完整上下文发我一下吗？或者告诉我这是做什么操作时报的？我继续查 🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":88,"output":527,"cacheRead":22272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22887,"cost":{"input":0.00001232,"output":0.00014756,"cacheRead":0.000623616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007834960000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780368056445,"responseId":"7e3f3531-937c-4f43-80ba-0931762abcd1"}}
